<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
    <h1 style="color: #2c3e50;">Borrow Request Denied</h1>

    <p>Hi {{ recipient.screenName }},</p>

    <p>Unfortunately, your request to borrow <strong>"{{ borrow.deck.name }}"</strong> for the event <strong>{{ borrow.event.name }}</strong> has been denied.</p>

    <p>You can browse other available decks for this event.</p>

    <p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <a href="{{ borrowUrl }}"
           style="background-color: #0d6efd; color: #ffffff; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block;">
            View Details
        </a>
    </p>

    <p>Or copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
    <p style="word-break: break-all; color: #666;">{{ borrowUrl }}</p>

    <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin: 30px 0;">
    <p style="color: #999; font-size: 12px;">Expanded Decks â€” Shared Pokemon TCG deck library</p>
</body>
</html>
